TITLE: Dynamically Registering Multiple ACF Blocks
DESCRIPTION: PHP function to dynamically register multiple ACF Blocks by iterating through the blocks directory.
SOURCE: https://github.com/timber/timber/blob/2.x/docs/v2/guides/gutenberg.md#2025-04-23_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
function register_acf_blocks() {
    foreach ($blocks = new DirectoryIterator( __DIR__ . '/blocks' ) as $item) {
        // Check if block.json file exists in each subfolder.
        if ($item->isDir() && !$item->isDot()
            && file_exists($item->getPathname() . '/block.json')
        ) {
            // Register the block given the directory name within the blocks
            // directory.
            register_block_type($item -> getPathname());
        }
    }
}

add_action('init', 'register_acf_blocks');
```

