CODE:
```
<nav>
    <ul class="nav-main">
        {% for item in menu.items %}
            <li class="nav-main-item {{ item.classes|join(' ') }}">
                <a class="nav-main-link" href="{{ item.link }}">{{ item.title }}</a>
