TITLE: Simple PHP Event Class with Date Display
DESCRIPTION: Basic Event class implementation with custom date display method for formatting event dates
SOURCE: https://github.com/timber/timber/blob/2.x/docs/v2/guides/extending-timber.md#2025-04-23_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
/**
 * Class Event
 */
class Event extends \Timber\Post
{
    /**
     * Gets display date.
     *
     * @return string
     */
    public function date_display($date_format = 'F j Y')
    {
        $date_start = DateTimeImmutable::createFromFormat('Ymd', $this->meta('date_start'));

        if (empty($date_start)) {
            return '';
        }

        return wp_date($date_format, $date_start->getTimestamp());
    }
}
```

