TITLE: Adding PSR-7 Request Object to Timber Context
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to add a PSR-7 request object to the Timber context using the Nyholm/psr7 library.
SOURCE: https://github.com/timber/timber/blob/2.x/docs/v2/upgrade-guides/2.0.md#2025-04-23_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
add_filter('timber/context', function($context) {
    $psr17Factory = new \Nyholm\Psr7\Factory\Psr17Factory();

    $creator = new \Nyholm\Psr7Server\ServerRequestCreator(
        $psr17Factory, // ServerRequestFactory
        $psr17Factory, // UriFactory
        $psr17Factory, // UploadedFileFactory
        $psr17Factory  // StreamFactory
    );

    $context['request'] = $creator->fromGlobals();

    return $context;
});
```

